                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/89212391/">shirley</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-06-25</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">西方的思维完全异与东方。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1206806899">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1206806899" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1206806899" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1206806899">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/138996064/">初枝雪音</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-06-24</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">我受到的震撼和感动绝不能用言语所形容，我获得的灵感和启发也不计其数，就文学上他也许只有荷马史诗可以与之相媲美。但是我却还是不得不违逆他，撒旦给人类下套，让人类感受到所谓神的压迫，专制，不平等，通过语言的诱惑创造所谓的禁忌，而使得人类反抗。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
